4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed to help individuals become cybersecurity specialists without prior knowledge. The program spans 16 weeks and includes three live online classes per week, with a maximum of 16 students per class. Participants will gain expertise in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, mastering cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence. The course also incorporates risk management and compliance with standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. Students receive an official completion certificate recognized by various institutions. The content is available in both English and Spanish. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop